ch_url": "https://github.com/pytorch/pytorch/pull/185.patch"}, "body_html": "<p><a class=\"user-mention\" data-hovercard-type=\"user\" data-hovercard-url=\"/hovercards?user_id=1310570\" data-octo-click=\"hovercard-link-click\" data-octo-dimensions=\"link_type:self\" href=\"https://github.com/soumith\">@soumith</a>, here are the changes I made to get ccache working with nvcc:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Install ccache 3.3</li>\n<li>Create a nvcc ccache symlink (<code>/usr/local/lib64/ccache/nvcc -&gt; ../../bin/ccache</code>)</li>\n<li>Set the environment variables <code>CUDA_TOOLKIT_ROOT_DIR=/usr/local/cuda/</code> and <code>CUDA_NVCC_EXECUTABLE=/usr/local/lib64/ccache/nvcc</code></li>\n</ul>", "body_text": "@soumith, here are the changes I made to get ccache working with nvcc:\n\nInstall ccache 3.3\nCreate a nvcc ccache symlink (/usr/local/lib64/ccache/nvcc -> ../../bin/ccache)\nSet the environment variables CUDA_TOOLKIT_ROOT_DIR=/usr/local/cuda/ and CUDA_NVCC_EXECUTABLE=/usr/local/lib64/ccache/nvcc", "body": "@soumith, here are the changes I made to get ccache working with nvcc:\r\n\r\n- Install ccache 3.3\r\n- Create a nvcc ccache symlink (`/usr/local/lib64/ccache/nvcc -> ../../bin/ccache`)\r\n- Set the environment variables `CUDA_TOOLKIT_ROOT_DIR=/usr/local/cuda/` and `CUDA_NVCC_EXECUTABLE=/usr/local/lib64/ccache/nvcc` "}